title: Ghost B.C. Bonus Tracks
description:
A set of all bonus tracks for the band Ghost (Ghost B.C. in the United States) released so far. Here's what you get:

- Here Comes the Sun (Beatles Cover)
- La Mantra Mori (Bonus Track)
- I'm a Marionette (ABBA cover)
- Waiting for The Night (Depeche Mode cover)
- If You Have Ghosts (Roky Erickson cover)

All files are tagged.

Please keep seeding after you complete your download so everyone can get this!
